pageContext.claim: “Now, the good thing is every single report -- as you know, Richard Burr came out -- Senator Richard Burr, head of the Senate Intelligence. They said, "Did you see any collusion?" "No collusion. I've seen no collusion whatsoever." Very strong.”
pageContext.analysis: Burr said the panel has found "no hard evidence of collusion," but continued the investigation "was not over" and they might find something they don't have today.
